307289089.name: XY—BREAKpoint
307289089.description: The hour grows desperate, and two worlds stand at the brink! The Pokémon TCG: XY—BREAKpoint expansion reveals the growing rift between the twin worlds, first discovered by Shiny Mega Gyarados-EX. Can they mend the rift and save both worlds from collision chaos?
